data.description: Adult home, childlike price, not a starter, widely nice, a true Capitol Hill bay in a truly Victorian way, restored architectural elements, urban farmhouse embellishments, more than two bedrooms, add a large den, then begin to explore, pine doors, painted floors, ceilings soaring, wood fire roaring, sunlight pouring over airy, carefree social space, a place your mom and dad would grace, the basements’ placement wins my race but the warm embrace of Lincoln Park, a Saturday stroll to Eastern Market, Trader Joe’s, three Metros, and on the list goes.
